---
import Stars from "../../assets/why-choose/stars.astro";
import Mountains from "../../assets/why-choose/mountains.astro";
import Sun from "../../assets/why-choose/sun.astro";
---
<section class="fade-in flex max-lg:flex-col justify-around items-center min-h-[75vh] px-8 lg:px-28 py-[2rem] lg:py-[6rem] text-white bg-black max-lg:mb-10" id="about-us">

    <div class="w-full max-w-[640px] lg:min-w-[580px] h-[400px] md:h-[580px] lg:mr-10">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-red-300 to-red-400 rounded-[9vw] lg:rounded-[6rem] h-full w-full p-2 lg:p-4">
            <div class="relative flex justify-center bg-black h-full w-full rounded-[9vw] lg:rounded-[5rem] overflow-hidden">
                <Stars />
                <Mountains />
                <Sun />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center max-w-[710px] max-lg:mt-10">
        <p class="text-white-200 font-epilogue font-bold text-3xl lg:text-[3rem] lg:leading-[3.6rem] max-w-[554px]">
            Why you should choose <h1 class="font-epilogue font-bold text-white-200 text-3xl lg:text-[3rem] lg:leading-[3.6rem]">Scarlet</h1>
        </p>
        <p class="text-white-200 text-md lg:text-[1.25rem] leading-[1.85rem] my-4">
            We offer a comprehensive suite of services, including web development, design, SEO, and social media marketing, 
            all aimed at helping your business reach new heights. Our tailored strategies are designed to deliver exceptional results 
            and elevate your brand. 
            <br /> <br />
            With our expertise in automation, we can streamline your operations, saving you time and resources. 
            <span class="underline text-white cursor-pointer hover:text-red-300 transition">Choose Scarlett</span> for a seamless and transformative 
            experience that will not only achieve your goals but also unlock your business's growth potential.
            <br /> <br />
            With expertise in web development, design, SEO, and social media marketing, we provide tailored strategies and exceptional results. 
            
        </p>
        <button id="about-contact-us" class="font-bold hover:bg-red-400 bg-red-300 text-white text-xl max-lg:w-full rounded lg:rounded-full py-4 px-16 mx-auto mt-5 lg:self-start transition">
            Contact Us
        </button>
    </div>
    <div>
        
    </div>
</section>
